com.interpss.core.aclf

Interface BaseAclfBus<TGen extends AclfGen,TLoad extends AclfLoad>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Bus, com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ExtensionElement, IAclfBus, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment, IAclfBusFunc, IAdaptable, IBusSwitchBreakModel, NameTag, NetworkedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AclfBus, AcscBus, BaseAcscBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseDStabBus<TGen,TLoad>, BaseOpfBus, BaseOpfGenBus, DclfOpfBus, DclfOpfGenBus, DStabBus, Dynamic3PBus, OpfBus, OpfGenBus, Steady3PBus
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfBusImpl, AcscBusImpl, BaseAclfBusImpl, BaseAcscBusImpl, BaseDStabBusImpl, BaseOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfBusImpl, DclfOpfGenBusImpl, DStabBusImpl, Dynamic3PBusImpl, OpfBusImpl, OpfGenBusImpl, Steady3PBusImpl

    public interface BaseAclfBus<TGen extends AclfGen,TLoad extends AclfLoad>
extends Bus, IAclfBus, IAclfBusFunc, IAclfBusAdaptation, IAclfBusAdjustment
    A representation of the model object 'Bus'. AclfBus class is for storing bus information for AC loadflow analysis. AclfBus could be extended using IAclfBus or ICustomLoad interface.

    The following features are supported:

    • Gen Code
    • Load Code
    • Voltage Mag
    • Voltage Ang
    • Desired Volt Mag
    • Desired Volt Ang
    • Gen P
    • Gen Q
    • Capacitor B
    • Load P
    • Load Q
    • Shunt Y
    • Exp Load P
    • Exp Load Q
    • QGen Limit
    • PGen Limit
    • VLimit
    • Load Dist Factor
    • Gen Part Factor
    • Dclf Inject P
    • Contribute Gen List
    • Contribute Load List
    • Function Load
    • Bus Control
    • Switched Shunt Device
    See Also:
    AclfPackage.getBaseAclfBus()
